fled from<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 his counterfeit<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 presence</l>
                    <l>As Gold the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Pyrites would<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 shun - </l>
                    <l>What confusion<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 would cover<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the innocent<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Jesus </l>
                    <l>To meet so<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
